name: A clear pipe holds no gunk, a free witch fears no mob.

metadata.name: A clear pipe holds no gunk, a free witch fears no mob.  1
metadata.description:
A video journal from first thing waking up this Monday morning (right before my weekly FT with CY). With every new week must come a new mint, so here I am reflecting on the phase of my creative journey I'm in: scrubbing clean my self-expression pipe by flowing creative artifacts freely and letting myself perform without "performing."

[cover image from museum photoshoot, by Em Tsui]
